P\Bigl(\bigcup_{i=1}^n A_i\Bigr)=p(1-p)^{n-1}+\dots+p^n-\sum_{j>i} (A_j\cap A_i)+\dots+(-1)^{n-1}P\Bigl(\bigcap A_i\Bigr).
A_i
P(\bigcup_{i = 1}^n A_i) = \sum_{k = 1}^n (-1)^{k - 1} \sum_{I ⊆ n, |I| = k} P(\bigcap_{i ∈ I} A_i) = \sum_{k = 1}^n (-1)^{k - 1} {n \choose k} p^k = 1 - (1 - p)^n
P(\bigcap_{i ∈ I} A_i) = p^{|I|}
